description:
Plastic surgeon Adam Kolker discusses all things boobs, including when medical insurance will pay for surgery, types of augmentations, different implants and their pros and cons, breasts growing back after surgery, and more. Plus, Jenn & Jess talk about hotel fragrances and the new “It” cream.
